&lt;p&gt;At GWI we&#39;re always looking for extraordinary people who thrive on making an extraordinary impact. Right now we&#39;re looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Insight Lead&lt;/strong&gt; to play a key role in our&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Insight Services&lt;/strong&gt; team in London. If that&#39;s you, and making a difference gets you out of bed in the morning, keep reading. It could be the start of something, well, extraordinary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sounds great, what will I be doing?&lt;/strong&gt; 🤔&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Insight Lead you’ll be passionate about uncovering data-driven stories that shape how the world’s biggest brands understand their audiences. In this role, you’ll turn GWI’s rich datasets into compelling insights, reports, and presentations that reveal the unexpected and make our clients’ strategies sharper.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;A few things you&#39;ll be responsible for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;👉 Lead end-to-end insight delivery on client projects across regions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;👉 Analyse GWI datasets and bespoke research studies to surface trends and patterns that align with client objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;👉 Create high-quality deliverables that translate complex data into clear, compelling narratives — and present them confidently to clients and internal teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;👉 Support the Vertical Lead on RFP responses, proposals, team operations, and mentoring junior analysts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;It&#39;s also fun; shaking things up is what working for GWI is all about. You&#39;ll need to be flexible, comfortable with continuous change, and working in a high-tempo environment.&lt;/p&gt;
