&lt;div class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;👉 Proven experience managing projects and clients.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;👉 A talent for data storytelling — translating numbers into narratives and surfacing insights that challenge assumptions or reveal something new.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;👉 Exceptional attention to detail and a flair for writing clear, engaging content.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;👉 Proficiency in Microsoft Office and Google Slides; experience with survey platforms or analytics tools is a plus.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;👉 Strong organisational and communication skills — comfortable running client presentations, managing multiple workstreams, and mentoring junior team members.&lt;/div&gt;
